title: The Mission
description: The mission is a mid-sized surf inspired swallowtail cruiser with an extended concave profile and a long wheelbase that make it ideal for cruising, carving banks, and mellow downhill. The true kicktail means no pile of dog poo, garden hose, or sleeping ho
